For Sara, her mother is her hero because she is the best mother and the best scientist in the world. But even your mother can't find a cure for the coronavirus. What is COVID-19? Sara asks her mom. “COVID - 19, or coronavirus, is a very small virus. Some symptoms are fever, cough, and shortness of breath, ”says her mother. How can we fight COVID-19? Sara asks We can all fight. Her mother says of Sara “Children are special and they can help too. You can be my hero, Sara "
